                <h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>Are you thinking of starting your own business? Or maybe you already have your own business are thinking about getting a new website?</p>
<p>Don't let the thought of having to pay hundreds or thousands of pounds for a website put you off getting one! A pay-monthly website may be exactly what you need. Check out how below:</p>
<img src="https://ashallendesign.ams3.digitaloceanspaces.com/public/blog/7/3-reasons-for-pay-monthly-website-design-infographic.png" alt="3 Reasons Why You Should Have a Pay-Monthly Website Design - Infographic Preston" class="py-4 img-fluid">
<h2>1. Affordable for start ups and small businesses.</h2>
<p>As a small business or a start up, you might not have a lot of money to invest in getting a website built; especially if you're just starting up. Getting a pay-monthly website, makes getting your own website affordable and accessible.</p>
<p>Our <a href="../services/website-design">pay-monthly websites</a> start from only £19.99 per month!</p>
<h2>2. No set up fees or hidden payments.</h2>
<p>With our <a href="../services/website-design">pay-monthly websites</a>, there are no set up fees or no hidden retainer fees. You pay a manageable, flat monthly fee each month that your site is live.</p>
<h2>3. No long term contracts or commitments.</h2>
<p>There's no need to worry about any long term contracts. Maybe you start to change your mind and feel like your business just isn't working out... That's OK, you can cancel your site without any cancellation fees. All of our pay-monthly websites run on a 30 day rolling contract basis.</p>
<h2>How Do I Get My Own Pay-Monthly Website?</h2>
<p>If you're interested in getting your own pay-monthly website, check out the <a href="../services/website-design">website design</a> page or cut straight to the chase and get in <a href="../contact">contact with me now</a>.</p>
<p class="text-center">
  <a href="../services/website-design" class="btn fill-style">
	Check Out The Website Design Service
  </a>
  <a href="../contact" class="btn fill-style">
	Contact Me Now
  </a>
</p>
